casebody.data:
No. 11-6668. Eusebio Escobar de Jesus, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1010, 132 S. Ct. 539,

181 L. Ed. 2d 389,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7632. October 31, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
